sql += "('" + id + "', '" + client_order_id + "', '" + created_at + "', '" + updated_at + "', '" + submitted_at + "', '" + asset_id + "', '" + symbol + "', '" + asset_class + "', '" + qty + "', '" + order_type + "', '" + type + "', '" + side + "', '" + time_in_force + "', '" + status + "', '" + subtag + "', '" + source + "', '" + extended_hours+ "','" +polygon_trade+ "','" +alpaca_price+ "'); "
